'''Roy L. Conrad''' ([[November 11]], [[1940s#1940|1940]] &ndash; [[January 18]], [[2002]])<ref name="Obituary" /> was an actor and voice actor, more commonly known among the [[LucasArts]] fandom as the voice of [[W:c:fullthrottle:Ben Throttle|Ben]] in the game ''Full Throttle'', alongside [[Mark Hamill]], who voiced the game's antagonist, [[W:c:fullthrottle:Adrian Ripburger|Adrian Ripburger]].

Conrad also voiced [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] pilot [[Ace Merrick]] in ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire]]''.

Conrad was most known for his deep and heavy voice, and died of lung cancer in 2002.<ref name="Obituary" />

